					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To summarize: there is only one set of sprites (4 tiles total) used for the flame, and the animation is accomplished solely by mirroring the graphic horizontally (by using the appropriate sprite attribute bit AND swapping the left and right halves).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
